// Audit checklist:
// 1. Is user input escaped in HTML context?
// 2. Is Content-Security-Policy header set?
// 3. Are dangerous functions (eval, innerHTML) avoided?
// 4. Is templating engine auto-escaping enabled?

// ❌ Vulnerable patterns
